<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#guard> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Indicates that the transitionFeature of a TransitionFeatureMembership is a guardExpression." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#guard> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#guardExpression> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
