<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#guardExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "TransitionUsage: The Expressions that define the guards of this TransitionUsage, which are the ownedFeatures of the TransitionUsage related to it by TransitionFeatureMemberships with kind = guard, which must all be Expressions." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#guardExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#ifArgument> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#ifArgument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "ifArgument" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#ifArgument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "IfActionUsage: The Expression whose result determines whether the thenAction or (optionally) the elseAction is performed. It is the first parameter of the IfActionUsage." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#ifArgument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
