<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importOwningNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Import: The Namespace into which Memberships are imported by this Import, which must be the owningRelatedElement of the Import." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importOwningNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedElement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "importedElement" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Import: The effectively imported Element for this Import. For a MembershipImport, this is the memberElement of the importedMembership. For a NamespaceImport, it is the importedNamespace." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "importedMembership" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Namespace: The Memberships in this Namespace that result from the ownedImports of this Namespace.\nMembershipImport: The Membership to be imported." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "importedNamespace" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "NamespaceImport: The Namespace whose visible Memberships are imported by this NamespaceImport." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#importedNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#in> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#FeatureDirectionKind> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#in> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "in" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#in> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Values of the Feature on each instance of its domain are determined externally to that instance and used internally." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#in> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#includedUseCase> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#includedUseCase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "includedUseCase" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#includedUseCase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "UseCaseUsage: The UseCaseUsages that are included by this UseCaseUse, which are the useCaseIncludeds of the IncludeUseCaseUsages owned by this UseCaseUsage.\nUseCaseDefinition: The UseCaseUsages that are included by this UseCaseDefinition, which are the useCaseIncludeds of the IncludeUseCaseUsages owned by this UseCaseDefinition." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#includedUseCase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
