<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#individualDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "individualDefinition" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#individualDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "OccurrenceUsage: The at most one occurrenceDefinition that has isIndividual = true." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#individualDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
