<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inheritedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Type: All the memberFeatures of the inheritedMemberships of this Type that are FeatureMemberships." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inheritedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inheritedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inheritedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "inheritedMembership" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inheritedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Type: All Memberships inherited by this Type via Specialization or Conjugation. These are included in the derived union for the memberships of the Type." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inheritedMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inout> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#FeatureDirectionKind> .
