<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inout> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Values of the Feature on each instance are determined either as in or out directions, or both." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#inout> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#input> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#input> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "input" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#input> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Type: All features related to this Type by FeatureMemberships that have direction in or inout." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#input> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#instantiatedType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
