<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeature> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningFeature" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Subsetting: A subsettingFeature that is also the owningRelatedElement of this Subsetting.\nFeatureTyping: A typedFeature that is also the owningRelatedElement of this FeatureTyping.\nFeatureInverting: A featureInverted that is also the owningRelatedElement of this FeatureInverting." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureMembership> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningFeatureMembership" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Feature: The FeatureMembership that owns this Feature as an ownedMemberFeature, determining its owningType." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureOfType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureOfType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningFeatureOfType" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureOfType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "TypeFeaturing: A featureOfType that is also the owningRelatedElement of this TypeFeaturing." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningFeatureOfType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningMembership> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
