<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Element: The owningRelationship of this Element, if that Relationship is a Membership." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningMembership> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningNamespace" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Element: The Namespace that owns this Element, which is the membershipOwningNamespace of the owningMembership of this Element, if any." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningNamespace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelatedElement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelatedElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningRelatedElement" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelatedElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relationship: The relatedElement of this Relationship that owns the Relationship, if any." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelatedElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelationship> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelationship> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningRelationship" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelationship> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Element: The Relationship for which this Element is an ownedRelatedElement, if any." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningRelationship> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningType" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specialization: The Type that is the specific Type of this Specialization and owns it as its owningRelatedElement.\nFeatureMembership: The Type that owns this FeatureMembership.\nFeature: The Type that is the owningType of the owningFeatureMembership of this Feature.\nConjugation: The conjugatedType of this Conjugation that is also its owningRelatedElement.\nDisjoining: A typeDisjoined that is also an owningRelatedElement." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningUsage> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "owningUsage" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Usage: The Usage in which this Usage is nested (if any)." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#owningUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#parameter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
