<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#referencedRendering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "referencedRendering" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#referencedRendering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "ViewRenderingMembership:  The RenderingUsage that is referenced through this ViewRenderingMembership. It is the referencedFeature of the ownedReferenceSubsetting for the ownedRendering, if there is one, and, otherwise, the ownedRendering itself." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#referencedRendering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
