<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#referencingFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "ReferenceSubsetting: The Feature that owns this ReferenceSubsetting relationship, which is also its subsettingFeature." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#referencingFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
