<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#referent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "FeatureReferenceExpression: The Feature that is referenced by this FeatureReferenceExpression, which is its first non-parameter member.\nAssignmentActionUsage: The Feature whose value is to be set." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#referent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
