<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "relatedFeature" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connector: The Features that are related by this Connector considered as a Relationship and that restrict the links it identifies, given by the referenced Features of the connectorEnds of the Connector." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "relatedType" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Association: The types of the associationEnds of the Association, which are the relatedElements of the Association considered as a Relationship." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#relatedType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#rendering> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#rendering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "rendering" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#rendering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "RenderingDefinition: The usages of a RenderingDefinition that are RenderingUsages." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#rendering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#renderingDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
