<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#renderingDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "RenderingUsage: The RenderingDefinition that is the definition of this RenderingUsage." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#renderingDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
