<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#result> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Expression: result.\nFunction: The object or value that is the result of evaluating the Function." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#result> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#resultExpression> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#resultExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "resultExpression" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#resultExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "AnalysisCaseUsage: An Expression used to compute the result of the AnalysisCaseUsage, owned via a ResultExpressionMembership.\nAnalysisCaseDefinition: An Expression used to compute the result of the AnalysisCaseDefinition, owned via a ResultExpressionMembership." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#resultExpression> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
