<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#source> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relationship: The relatedElements from which this Relationship is considered to be directed.\nTransitionUsage: The source ActionUsage of this TransitionUsage, which becomes the source of the succession for the TransitionUsage." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#source> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#sourceFeature> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
