<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#sourceFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connector: The source relatedFeature for this Connector. It is the first relatedFeature." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#sourceFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#sourceOutputFeature> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#sourceOutputFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "sourceOutputFeature" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#sourceOutputFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Flow: The Feature that provides the items carried by the Flow. It must be a feature of the source of the Flow." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#sourceOutputFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
