<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#viewpointStakeholder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "ViewpointUsage: The PartUsages that identify the stakeholders with concerns framed by this ViewpointUsage, which are the owned and inherited stakeholderParameters of the framedConcerns of this ViewpointUsage.\nViewpointDefinition: The PartUsages that identify the stakeholders with concerns framed by this ViewpointDefinition, which are the owned and inherited stakeholderParameters of the framedConcerns of this ViewpointDefinition." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#viewpointStakeholder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#visibility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#visibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "visibility" .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#visibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Membership: Whether or not the Membership of the memberElement in the membershipOwningNamespace is publicly visible outside that Namespace.\nImport: The visibility level of the imported members from this Import relative to the importOwningNamespace. The default is private." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#visibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/sysml/vocabulary#> .
